  Azure Arc Onboarding Monitor
  Unified framework for onboarding servers to Azure Arc
  Supports: VMware | Azure Local | Hyper-V | Physical | KVM | Nutanix

  ========================================================================

  SELECT MODE:

    [1]  Onboard Servers to Azure Arc (Recommended)
         Enter targets  ->  PreReq check  ->  Install  ->  Connect
         Live TUI dashboard opens in a separate monitor window

    [2]  PreReq Check Only
         Validate remote servers without onboarding

    [3]  Setup Wizard
         Create Service Principal, configure Azure identity

    [4]  Test Network Connectivity
         Test Azure Arc endpoint reachability from REMOTE target servers

    [Q]  Quit

